{
  "stem": "1736.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I followed those people, and of course what I saw was the synagogue being attacked with stones and all sorts of things, and-- and the [INAUDIBLE] being wrecked, the [INAUDIBLE] being pulled out.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there's many books been written about Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think that I have to say [INAUDIBLE] barely to say that--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The place was burned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To my delight, I found out later on that two of the people actually got killed in the process.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this is just part of, you know, the-- of what went on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after having watched this for a while, I got on my bike because I saw them moving over to another place which was also not far from there and destroying a shopfront.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It then occurred to me that because I knew a lot of other people in the city, that I should at least try and warn them to get out and proceeded to do that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On my own.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I got onto my bike.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to a couple of places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I distinctly remember going to a place, number eight [GERMAN], where there was a Jewish furrier who had a-- and they were relatives, distant relatives.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I raced up the stairs and told them to get out and ask questions, which they did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, within 15 minutes, the mob had arrived, and we could see them throwing the furniture out of the second floor, and the-- and the clothing and all this sort of thing and move on",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
